{
  "texts": [
    "When assigning tasks, consider the following factors: 1.",
    "**Agent's Current State:** This includes the agent's location, items in possession, health status, etc. 2.",
    "**Task Requirements:** Necessary items, task location, and other specific needs. 3.",
    "**Agent's Experience:** Previous tasks completed and overall performance history. 4.",
    "**Agent's Abilities:** Skills and capabilities relevant to the task."
  ]
}